<div class="landscaping-jobs">
  <section class="landscaping-hero">
    <p class="landscaping-eyebrow">Touching Grass... Yours.</p>
    <h1 class="mt-0">AW Lawn & Landscape</h1>
    <p class="landscaping-hero-intro">
      The internet told us to "go touch grass" and we took it literally. Expect crisp edges, clean
      beds, and a yard that looks dialed-in, all while you enjoy your weekend.
    </p>
    <div class="landscaping-hero-actions">
      <%= link_to "Contact us", contact_path, class: "landscaping-cta-button" %>
      <span class="landscaping-hero-note">Fast Quotes | Tidy, Scheduled Work | Satisfaction Guaranteed</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="landscaping-highlights">
    <div class="landscaping-highlight-card">
      <h2>One-time resets</h2>
      <p>Move-outs, post-party recoveries, or that "we'll do it later" yard that needs it now. We handle projects of all sizes with care and attention to detail.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="landscaping-highlight-card">
      <h2>Maintenance that sticks</h2>
      <p>Weekly or seasonal plans that keep curb appeal consistent throughout the diverse seasons we face here in the Pacific Northwest.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="landscaping-highlight-card">
      <h2>Details matter</h2>
      <p>Grass, shrubs, gravel, and parking strips handled with clean lines, service on time, and a commitment to quality backed by years of professional service.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="landscaping-services">
    <h2>Services we handle</h2>
    <%= render "services" %>
  </section>

  <section class="landscaping-work">
    <div class="landscaping-work-header">
      <h2>Recent yard recoveries</h2>
      <p>Small snapshots of clean lines, fresh beds, and revived paths.</p>
    </div>
    <%= render "jobs", jobs: @LandscapingJobs %>
  </section>
</div>
